  "clauseRiskSummary": "This clause defines the product name for the joint venture, but lacks details on operational responsibilities or financial arrangements.",
  "operative_text": "4. PRODUCT NAME: \"PRINTED LIGHT SHEETS\" is the name and title CLIENT will use to market for Nano Printed Lights.\n",
  "concerns": [
